member.name: M:common_bios_pxeboot_default.common_bios_pxeboot_default.Run
member.summary: If the test status is "New", then set the test status to "pxe boot" and reboot the system. If the test status is "pxe boot", then run the powershell script to check the bios version. If the bios version is matched, then set the test result to "Pass". If the bios version is not matched, then set the test result to "Fail".
